      "review_disposition": "retain_current_post_compaction_quality_revision_and_reflow_semantic_sentences",
      "requires_candidate_text_change": true,
      "historical_manual_compact_ko": "\u001bCA히데요시\u001bCZ는 천하 위해\n\u001bCB[bs1871]가\u001bCZ를 방치 못 해\n\u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ 포섭.",
      "legacy_complete_ko": "\u001bCA히데요시\u001bCZ는, 천하인을 노리는 데 있어,\n거대한 존재감을 유지하는 \u001bCB[bs1871]가\u001bCZ를 방치할 수 없다. 수단 방법을 가리지 않고, \u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ 포섭을 꾀했다.",
      "current_ko": "천하인을 목표로 한 \u001bCA히데요시\u001bCZ는\n거대한 존재감을 유지하는 \u001bCB[bs1871]가\u001bCZ를\n그대로 둘 수 없었다. 수단을 가리지 않고\n\u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ 포섭을 꾀했다.",
      "proposed_ko": "천하인을 목표로 한 \u001bCA히데요시\u001bCZ는\n거대한 존재감을 유지하는 \u001bCB[bs1871]가\u001bCZ를\n그대로 둘 수 없었다.\n수단을 가리지 않고 \u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ 포섭을 꾀했다.",
      "text_hashes_utf16le_sha256": {
        "legacy_complete_ko": "9BD38E66EAEB8C9C4FE54A75BDC95C35659B14A2411977BC926E724BFDC8A741",
        "current_ko": "2DA38D591D23C54C1C0CB8157CEDE243A6C1E1E20BFE9F51D133AA0C28FB9275",
        "proposed_ko": "423A3378B5DB32AE046F577DF28A47C2728F6E6875171E0F6F7A56101985E273"
      },
      "direct_pc_source_evidence": {
        "jp": "\u001bCA秀吉\u001bCZは、天下人を目指す上で、\n巨大な存在感を保つ\u001bCB[bs1871]家\u001bCZを放置できない。なりふりかまわず、\u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ取り込みを図った。",
        "en": "\u001bCAHideyoshi\u001bCZ, determined to become the grand unifier, could not afford to ignore the towering presence of the \u001bCB[bs1871] Clan\u001bCZ. Undeterred by how his actions might be perceived, he began plotting to win them over.",
        "sc": "\u001bCA秀吉\u001bCZ既然剑指天下人，\n就不可能任极富存在感的\u001bCB[bs1871]家\u001bCZ自由发展。\n他不顾一切，企图笼络\u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ。",
        "tc": "\u001bCA秀吉\u001bCZ既以天下人為目標，\n自然無法忽視佔有一席之地的\u001bCB[bs1871]家\u001bCZ。\n因此不顧一切，試圖籠絡\u001bCB[bm1871]\u001bCZ。",
        "utf16le_sha256": {
          "jp": "CCC73DC27F6E2AC632C9C3D6E50E0614F465436A01AA857B6D6DE63F71042C71",
          "en": "8A51DED91613B98797203819E52D92E74067BCA111392D294E476A0AAED7756F",
          "sc": "57A935AA3C9529DE5CBFBA8B53E4926EBF17634670AF6D38131804FF507D7317",
          "tc": "42DEED4B1DF7BCEE4E6917A0A06BA81A289ECC2C2AB82175A07EAEEDF0DAB574"
